@startuml Speech Notetaker Outline

actor User

User --> (Program Begins) : Launch application

(Program Begins) --> (UI Display) : Main Thread\nInitialize UI
(Program Begins) --> (Microphone) : Main Thread\nInitialize audio thread
(Program Begins) --> (Real-Time Transcription) : Main Thread\nInitialize transcription thread


User --> (Microphone) : User speaks

(Microphone) --> (Audio Queue) : Thread 1\nSend audio chunks

(Audio Queue) --> (Real-Time Transcription) : Thread 2\nOpneAI Whisper transcribes
(Real-Time Transcription) --> (Text Queue) : Thread 2\nSend text chunks

(Text Queue) --> (UI Display) : Main Thread\nAppend text in real time

(UI Display) --> (Cleaned Notes) : When Stopped\nSend full transcript to Ollama Phi-3\nwith custom prompt
(Cleaned Notes) --> (Save Text) : Option to save cleaned notes to .txt file

package "Notes" {
  (Python 3.10 / 3.11 supported)
  (Ollama Phi-3 on local machine)
}

@enduml
